---

<BaseLayout
  title="At-Home Personal Trainer Lake Mary | Mobile Personal Training Heathrow FL | Come To You Fitness"
  description="Professional in-home personal training in Lake Mary, Heathrow, and Longwood FL. Certified mobile fitness coaches bring custom workouts to your door. Results guaranteed or your money back."
  keywords="at-home personal trainer Lake Mary, mobile personal training Heathrow FL, in-home fitness coach Longwood, personal training near Lake Mary FL, fitness trainer comes to you Longwood FL"
>
  <Navigation />

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <h1>Professional Personal Training ‚Äî Delivered to Your Door</h1>
        <p class="hero-subtitle">Expert fitness coaching, custom programming, and lasting results ‚Äî all from the comfort of your own home in Lake Mary, Heathrow, Longwood, and Sanford, FL.</p>
        <div class="hero-buttons">
          <a href="tel:407-706-2272" class="btn btn-primary">Call 407-706-2272</a>
          <a href="#consultation" class="btn btn-outline">Free Consultation</a>
        </div>
        <p class="guarantee-badge">‚úì Results Guaranteed or Your Money Back</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Choose Section -->
  <section class="why-choose">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Why Come To You Fitness?</h2>
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature">
          <div class="feature-icon">üèãÔ∏è</div>
          <h3>20+ Years of Expertise</h3>
          <p>Led by Allen Linville, our nationally certified trainers specialize in sports performance, strength training, rehabilitation, and corrective exercise.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
          <div class="feature-icon">üè†</div>
          <h3>Training at Your Doorstep</h3>
          <p>No gym hassle. No commute. We bring professional equipment and expert coaching directly to your home.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
          <div class="feature-icon">üìã</div>
          <h3>5-Step Success System</h3>
          <p>Our proven "5 Steps to Achieving Your Health and Fitness Goals" program ensures sustainable, measurable results.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
          <div class="feature-icon">üí™</div>
          <h3>Customized Programs</h3>
          <p>Every session is tailored to your goals, fitness level, and any movement limitations ‚Äî evolving as you progress.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Services Overview -->
  <section class="services-overview">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Specialized Training Programs</h2>
      <p class="section-intro">Whether you're building strength, losing weight, or recovering from injury, we have a program designed for you.</p>

      <div class="services-grid">
        <a href="/services/strength-training" class="service-card">
          <h3>Strength Training</h3>
          <p>Build muscle, increase power, and improve overall strength with progressive resistance programs.</p>
        </a>

        <a href="/services/weight-loss" class="service-card">
          <h3>Weight Loss & Fat Loss</h3>
          <p>Sustainable fat-burn training and body transformation programs that deliver real results.</p>
        </a>

        <a href="/services/functional-training" class="service-card">
          <h3>Functional & Athletic Training</h3>
          <p>Enhance mobility, performance, and conditioning for sports and everyday life.</p>
        </a>

        <a href="/services/busy-professionals" class="service-card">
          <h3>For Busy Professionals</h3>
          <p>Efficient 30-45 minute sessions that fit your schedule ‚Äî before work, during lunch, or after hours.</p>
        </a>

        <a href="/services/parents" class="service-card">
          <h3>For Parents</h3>
          <p>Stay fit while your kids are home. No childcare needed when your workout comes to you.</p>
        </a>

        <a href="/services/over-35" class="service-card">
          <h3>For Over-35s & Mature Adults</h3>
          <p>Age-appropriate training focused on mobility, strength, and vitality for long-term health.</p>
        </a>

        <a href="/services/post-rehab" class="service-card">
          <h3>Post-Rehab & Injury Prevention</h3>
          <p>Safe, effective training for clients recovering from injury or managing chronic pain.</p>
        </a>

        <a href="/services/coaching" class="service-card">
          <h3>Coaching & Accountability</h3>
          <p>Ongoing support, progress tracking, and motivation to keep you on track toward your goals.</p>
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="cta-center">
        <a href="/services" class="btn btn-secondary">View All Services</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How It Works -->
  <section class="how-it-works">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Our 5-Step Process</h2>
      <div class="steps-grid">
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-number">1</div>
          <h3>Consultation</h3>
          <p>We discuss your goals, challenges, and fitness history in a no-pressure conversation.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-number">2</div>
          <h3>Assessment</h3>
          <p>Comprehensive movement evaluation identifies strengths, limitations, and areas of focus.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-number">3</div>
          <h3>Custom Program Design</h3>
          <p>Your personalized training plan is built around your specific goals and current fitness level.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-number">4</div>
          <h3>Guided Training</h3>
          <p>30-45 minute sessions that challenge you safely and efficiently, with expert coaching every step.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-number">5</div>
          <h3>Progress & Adaptation</h3>
          <p>Your program evolves as your body adapts, ensuring continuous improvement and results.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Service Areas -->
  <section class="service-areas">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Serving Central Florida</h2>
      <p class="section-intro">Proudly bringing professional in-home personal training to these communities:</p>

      <div class="locations-grid">
        <a href="/locations/lake-mary" class="location-card">
          <h3>Lake Mary Personal Training</h3>
          <p>Mobile personal training and in-home fitness coaching for Lake Mary residents.</p>
        </a>

        <a href="/locations/heathrow" class="location-card">
          <h3>Heathrow Personal Training</h3>
          <p>At-home strength training and conditioning programs in Heathrow, FL.</p>
        </a>

        <a href="/locations/longwood" class="location-card">
          <h3>Longwood Personal Training</h3>
          <p>In-home fitness coaching and functional training for Longwood clients.</p>
        </a>
      </div>

      <p class="also-serving">Also serving Sanford and surrounding areas</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="cta-section" id="consultation">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Ready to Transform Your Fitness?</h2>
      <p>Start with a free consultation and movement assessment. No pressure, no obligation ‚Äî just expert guidance.</p>
      <div class="cta-buttons">
        <a href="tel:407-706-2272" class="btn btn-primary btn-large">Call 407-706-2272</a>
        <a href="mailto:support@cometoyoufitness.com" class="btn btn-outline btn-large">Email Us</a>
      </div>
      <p class="guarantee-text">‚úì Results Guaranteed or Your Money Back</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* Hero Section */
  .hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #37ca37 0%, #2db92d 100%);
    color: var(--white);
    padding: 5rem 0;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .hero-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .guarantee-badge {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--primary-orange);
    background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 2rem;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  /* Why Choose Section */
  .why-choose {
    padding: 4rem 0;
    background-color: #f7fafc;
  }

  .why-choose h2 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    color: var(--dark-gray);
  }

  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .feature {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2rem;
    background-color: var(--white);
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }

  .feature:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
  }

  .feature-icon {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .feature h3 {
    color: var(--primary-green);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  /* Services Overview */
  .services-overview {
    padding: 4rem 0;
  }

  .services-overview h2 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .section-intro {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--medium-gray);
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto 3rem;
  }

  .services-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .service-card {
    padding: 2rem;
    background-color: var(--white);
    border: 2px solid var(--light-gray);
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--dark-gray);
  }

  .service-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--primary-green);
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(55, 202, 55, 0.2);
  }

  .service-card h3 {
    color: var(--primary-green);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .cta-center {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  /* How It Works */
  .how-it-works {
    padding: 4rem 0;
    background-color: #f7fafc;
  }

  .how-it-works h2 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .steps-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .step {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .step-number {
    width: 60px;
    height: 60px;
    background-color: var(--primary-green);
    color: var(--white);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0 auto 1rem;
  }

  .step h3 {
    color: var(--dark-gray);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  /* Service Areas */
  .service-areas {
    padding: 4rem 0;
  }

  .service-areas h2 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .locations-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .location-card {
    padding: 2rem;
    background-color: var(--white);
    border: 2px solid var(--light-gray);
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--dark-gray);
  }

  .location-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--primary-orange);
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(246, 173, 85, 0.2);
  }

  .location-card h3 {
    color: var(--primary-green);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .also-serving {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--medium-gray);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  /* CTA Section */
  .cta-section {
    padding: 4rem 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--dark-gray) 0%, var(--medium-gray) 100%);
    color: var(--white);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cta-section h2 {
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .cta-section p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .btn-large {
    padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .guarantee-text {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--primary-orange);
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .hero-subtitle {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .hero-buttons {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .hero-buttons .btn {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 300px;
    }

    .services-grid,
    .locations-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .steps-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
